name: StillsFromLastNight #08b — 🟢
description:
The Stills from Last Night are selected outputs from the nightly experiments with code. That night, a broad idea of introducing abstract, 2D patterns entwined with the vegetation was initially sketched with a basic round shape. It was by forgetting that the round shape must be the least abstract shape there is in Nature, the way our eyes picture it. Round is the planet or the atom. It is Moon as much as it is Sun. It's the perfect equilibrium of forces.
Round is protection — it's the shell of the egg before it breaks and opens up to the possibilities. Or chaos.

—

— Generative drawing
— Made with Javascript code
— Format PNG
— Resolution 6000x6000
